{"tid":811804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做design嘅有無人同我一樣習慣？","createTime":"2018-09-09T06:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T09:32:26.000Z","uid":141237,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"004659b57601675cd4751c3ecf655b367284d849","tid":811804,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"因為我仲係讀緊書，算係半parttime去做，<br />\n好多時候都係放假紅日先會真正去搞。<br />\n<br />\n我當一日全日都stay係屋企，<br />\n我既安排會係朝頭早一邊上下網，一邊睇d references，比如可能會睇下youtube，睇下d綜藝節目，聽下電台鬼故，先再睇睇d有關既references，或者一邊聽一邊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為有時覺得就咁睇references真係會太無聊，而且依d嘢唔係睇一個鐘兩個鐘...會睇半日，甚至一日，有時又未必即刻諗到d構思出黎，可能我自己問題。<br />\n<br />\n跟住通常咁搞下搞下到到夜晚，可能6點幾，或者食完晚飯先開始去試ideas，開始著手去畫。<br />\n<br />\nps新手，自己覺得有時8分時間睇references，2分時間完成個idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁，定還是只有我奇怪。"},{"pid":"cdce1c915fea2f5f73a77c92984fd343b7103723","tid":811804,"uid":96815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時仲會一日訓幾次覺睇下訓醒會唔會有靈感 頹到有靈感出現"},{"pid":"d9e1a6ff7c2dcb88f39703a5e301d727ac89b149","tid":811804,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda9eba049ac3677392de324183e7266d11c6d4f","tid":811804,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdce1c915fea2f5f73a77c92984fd343b7103723","tid":811804,"uid":96815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時仲會一日訓幾次覺睇下訓醒會唔會有靈感 頹到有靈感出現"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"我又唔會刻意訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至有時會突登早起，虐待下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo